        <abstract>
            <p>Faraday memorial is an exception.</p> 
<p>George [Darwin] has convinced CD that <hi rend="italic">North British Review</hi> article is by P. G. Tait [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">6841</hi>].</p>  
<p>Surprised that leaves of <hi rend="italic">Drosophyllum</hi> are always rolled backwards at their tips, but did not know it was unique character.</p> 
